&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle from initial outreach and discovery through close, positioning SPINS as a commerce enablement and Anywhere Commerce partner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead consultative conversations focused on shopper discovery, product availability, and conversion across owned, paid, and retailer environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
