&lt;li&gt;Execute multi‑channel outreach strategies across email, phone, LinkedIn, and events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage inbound leads, marketing programs, retailer interest, and internal referrals to supplement outbound activity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain consistent activity levels and strong follow‑through to convert interest into qualified opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
